      "wikipedia_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missa_Puer_natus_est_nobis",
      "wikipedia_extract": "Missa Puer natus est nobis is a mass setting composed by Thomas Tallis. It is one of three complete masses by Tallis. It was sung by the joint Capilla Flamenca and Chapel Royal choirs in Christmas 1554, during which Philip of Spain was in England.",
